es/news201802092636.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kmb.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fpress%2Farchives%2Fnews201802092636.html&d=i39qNLC40jzU861zNgQnlr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f82d553d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.kmb.hk/tc/news/press/archives/news201802092636.html</a><br />\n<br />\n「九巴月票」適用於全港逾四百條路線*，包括常規路線、馬場專線、通宵線、口岸線以及假日特別線。其中，跨公司的聯營過海線亦納入月票計劃，<span style=\"color: red;\">乘客可憑「九巴月票」乘搭由九巴提供的班次</span>。<br />\n<br />\n明明發稿時已經寫明限制，咁都話九巴冇講....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54431a96ce7d6c097852db613fc4b5c3d1c7db14","tid":580561,"uid":81052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ab594fb344530fb8e2b2ac10238e84fb876b5c1","tid":580561,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f25a105a49c78468f2da11c7bb6e9f06bb4a33a2","tid":580561,"uid":81052,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0f3d4ccf61992b818d49b8598bacae14033a0d48","tid":580561,"uid":37661,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"蠢過閪，求其搵班車過咗海先，再轉咪有車囉。<br />\n<br />\n平時坐開都知有分九巴城巴時段架啦，咁都仲買真係戇撚鳩。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"之前先見有人撐九巴月票係德政,係專俾搭開過海車既人用<br />\n話唔明點解唔過海既人冇著數就走去屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"你睇下大西北 960 961 968收緊幾錢同埋邊間巴士公司做先啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T01:48:50.000Z","msg":"其實想表達咩呢，得大西北既人要過海咩?定得大西北搭巴士貴?<br />\n<br />\n九巴俾人屌賺錢都仲不停加價，之後先出月票<br />\n但係票價又貴，數字上係過海車先抵<br />\n實際上仲要扣埋聯營路線(或者要計到準一準先搭)"},{"pid":"85f34630437eacad5dcd1eba9bac0580f86baa38","tid":580561,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T01:50:24.000Z","msg":"好快會出埋聯營月票，又貴多一筆"},{"pid":"97b09aa0c4a3b541a9fdafe6a19283b37138a0b9","tid":580561,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"516a47bd1f05c064ab9ac00829a882c38fc5b285","tid":